        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong>mix eggs with sugar
</p>
<p><strong>Step 2:</strong>after that add milk there
</p>
<p><strong>Step 3:</strong>after that add flour and mix it 1 min
</p>
<p><strong>Step 4:</strong>add oil there and mix it 1 min
</p>
<p><strong>Step 5:</strong>heat the stove and fry pancakes on it
</p>

